snippet.textDisplay: So so so overwhelmed after watching this song. It is not just a song for me it's a celebration of who we are. As a Sindhi every emotion portrayed in this song touches the chords of my heart and makes me wanna watch this again and again. Thank u coke studio for making this track possible. Thank u to everyone who was involved in the making of this song. I couldn't be happier that our Sindhi music, our Sindhi culture is getting the recognition it deserves and the song is sooo good even as an audio that u get hooked pretty soon even if u don't really know Sindhi. They have done a fabulous job in every department whether it is choosing sindhi rap by Babar mangi or the lyrics. The usage of chung.. or the powerful vocals of saiban and marvi. This song will always remain very very very special to me till the day I exist as it is an extension of who I identify myself to be . Thank u from the bottom of my heart ❤️ coke studio
